Update the ClickUp task for this work using the MCP integration. Follow these steps:
1. First, search ClickUp to find the relevant task (use task name or ID if known)
2. Update the task status to reflect current progress (e.g., "in progress", "in review", "complete")
3. Add a comment summarizing what was accomplished in this session
4. Include specific details: files changed, features implemented, bugs fixed
5. If the task is blocked, update status and add a comment explaining the blocker
6. Update time tracking if applicable
7. If new subtasks were discovered, create them under the main task
8. Link any relevant commits or PRs in the comment
9. Assign to the next person if handoff is needed
